comments: Bagley III (DET) establishes himself in Bridges' (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Knox II (DET) moves alongside Booker's (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) makes contact with the ball when it is outside of the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring.
Craig (PHX) is moving alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Bagley III (DET) has his arm slightly extended and marginal contact occurs with Craig (PHX) during the pick.
Craig (PHX) is late to establish himself in a legal guarding position within Burks' (DET) path and makes contact to his body, which affects Burks' driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) firms up in Bogdanovic's (DET) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the pick.
Bagley III (DET) legally contests and cleanly blocks Payne's (PHX) shot attempt.
Craig (PHX) moves slightly toward Bogdanovic (DET) and marginal contact occurs as they come together on the perimeter.
Ayton (PHX) moves alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the driving shot attempt.
Hayes (DET) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Craig (PHX) prior to incidental follow-through arm contact occurring.
Craig (PHX) steps on Bogdanovic's (DET) foot, which affects his SQBR as he starts to move up the court.
Bridges (PHX) is moving alongside Burks' (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Ayton (PHX) receives the pass in the backcourt prior to moving into the frontcourt and establishing positive frontcourt position.
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Ayton (PHX).
Booker (PHX) legally contests Livers' (DET) jump shot attempt.
